47:39.107 --> 47:40.525
You shouldn't be here.

47:41.734 --> 47:42.944
I know.

47:44.362 --> 47:46.698
If you leave right now,
I won't say anything.

47:46.698 --> 47:49.200
- I swear.
- I can't do that.

47:53.705 --> 47:55.456
You need to admit what you did.

47:57.750 --> 47:59.168
Who you are.

48:03.131 --> 48:05.842
I am not that man.

48:05.842 --> 48:07.468
You are.

48:09.512 --> 48:12.515
Admit who you are.

48:14.851 --> 48:16.060
I can't.

48:22.859 --> 48:25.570
You're gonna have to do this.

48:27.363 --> 48:29.741
You understand me?

48:35.371 --> 48:37.123
- I won't.
