48:39.667 --> 48:43.129
You are a Christian woman, yes?

48:47.008 --> 48:49.636
He would not
want you to do this.

48:51.429 --> 48:53.598
You are not a killer.

48:53.598 --> 48:55.600
You are a woman of God.

49:26.881 --> 49:30.093
Fuck. Fuck, fuck.

